#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="146"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.679"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs5.1.7"
msgid ""
"Tīhākārehi … pe … sattahākārehi paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajjinti vattukāmo "
"suññataṃ vimokkhaṃ …"
msgstr ""
"If he lies in full awareness, meaning to say, “I attained the first "
"absorption,” while actually saying, “I attained the emptiness release …"

