"absorption,” while actually saying, “I attained the second absorption,” "
"then, if the listener understands, he commits an offense entailing expulsion "
"when three conditions are fulfilled;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs5.4.16"
msgid "na paṭi­vijānan­tassa āpatti thullaccayassa."
msgstr ""
"if the listener does not understand, he commits a serious offense when three "
"conditions are fulfilled."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="158"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.691"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs5.4.17"
msgid ""
"Tīhākārehi … pe … sattahākārehi mohā ca me cittaṃ vinīvaraṇaṃ paṭhamañca "
"jhānaṃ dutiyañca jhānaṃ tatiyañca jhānaṃ catutthañca jhānaṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""
