msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.10.9"
msgid "Taṃ bhikkhū etadavocuṃ—"
msgstr "The monks said to him,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.10.10"
msgid "“kaccāvuso, khamanīyaṃ, kacci yāpanīyan”ti?"
msgstr "“We hope you’re bearing up, we hope you’re comfortable?”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.10.11"
msgid "“Nāvuso, sakkā puthujjanena adhivāsetun”ti."
msgstr "“It’s not possible for an ordinary person to endure this.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.10.12"
msgid "Tassa kukkuccaṃ ahosi … pe …"
msgstr "He became remorseful …"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.10.13"
msgid "“kiṃcitto tvaṃ, bhikkhū”ti?"
msgstr "“What was your intention, monk?”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.10.14"
msgid "“Ullapa­nā­dhip­pāyo ahaṃ, bhagavā”ti."
msgstr "“I intended to make a claim, Master.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.10.15"
msgid "“Anāpatti, bhikkhu, pārājikassa;"
msgstr "“There’s no offense entailing expulsion,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.10.16"
msgid "āpatti thullaccayassā”ti."
msgstr "but there’s a serious offense.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.10.17"
msgid "(23)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="200"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-pj.4.8.11"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.733"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.11.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena aññataro brāhmaṇo bhikkhū nimantetvā etadavoca—"
msgstr "At one time a brahmin invited the monks:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.11.2"
msgid "“āyantu bhonto arahanto”ti."
msgstr "“Let the good sirs, the perfected ones, come.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.11.3"
msgid "Tesaṃ kukkuccaṃ ahosi—"
msgstr "They became remorseful and said,"

#. VAR: na arahanto → anarahanto (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.11.4"
msgid "“mayañcamha na arahanto."
msgstr "“We’re not perfected ones,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.11.5"
msgid "Ayañca brāhmaṇo amhe arahantavādena samudācarati."
msgstr "and yet this brahmin speaks to us as if we were."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.11.6"
msgid "Kathaṃ nu kho amhehi paṭi­pajji­tabban”ti?"
msgstr "What should we do?”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.11.7"
msgid "Bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ."
msgstr "They told the Master."

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.11.8"
msgid "“Anāpatti, bhikkhave, pasādabhaññe”ti."
msgstr "“There’s no offense when something is spoken in faith.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.11.9"
msgid "(24)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="201"></a><a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.179"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.734"></a> 
