msgid "Tena kho pana samayena aññataro brāhmaṇo bhikkhū nimantetvā etadavoca—"
msgstr "At one time a brahmin invited the monks:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.11.11"
msgid "“nisīdantu bhonto arahanto”ti …"
msgstr "“Let the good sirs, the perfected ones, be seated …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.11.12"
msgid "“bhuñjantu bhonto arahanto”ti …"
msgstr "Let the good sirs, the perfected ones, eat …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.11.13"
msgid "“tappentu bhonto arahanto”ti …"
msgstr "Let the good sirs, the perfected ones, be satisfied …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.11.14"
msgid "“gacchantu, bhonto arahanto”ti."
msgstr "Let the good sirs, the perfected ones, go.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.11.15"
msgid "Tesaṃ kukkuccaṃ ahosi—"
msgstr "They became remorseful and said,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.11.16"
msgid "“mayañcamha na arahanto."
msgstr "“We’re not perfected ones,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.11.17"
msgid "Ayañca brāhmaṇo amhe arahantavādena samudācarati."
msgstr "and yet this brahmin speaks to us as if we were."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.11.18"
msgid "Kathaṃ nu kho amhehi paṭi­pajji­tabban”ti?"
msgstr "What should we do?”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.11.19"
msgid "Bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ."
msgstr "They told the Master."

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.11.20"
msgid "“Anāpatti, bhikkhave, pasādabhaññe”ti."
msgstr "“There’s no offense when something is spoken in faith.”"

