#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="207"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.740"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.13.13"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena aññataraṃ bhikkhuṃ ñātakā etadavocuṃ—"
msgstr "At one time the relatives of a certain monk said to him,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.13.14"
msgid "“abhiramasi, bhante”ti?"
msgstr "“Come, Venerable, enjoy yourself.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.13.15"
msgid "“Abhirato ahaṃ, āvuso, paramāya abhiratiyā”ti."
msgstr "“I’m enjoying myself with the highest enjoyment.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.13.16"
msgid "Tassa kukkuccaṃ ahosi."
msgstr "He became remorseful,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.13.17"
msgid "“Ye kho te bhagavato sāvakā te evaṃ vadeyyuṃ."
msgstr "thinking, “Those who are true disciple of the Master may say that,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.13.18"
msgid "Ahañcamhi na bhagavato sāvako."
msgstr "but I’m not such a disciple."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.13.19"
msgid "Kacci nu kho ahaṃ pārājikaṃ āpattiṃ āpanno”ti?"
msgstr "Could it be that I’ve committed an offense entailing expulsion?”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.13.20"
msgid "Bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesi."
msgstr "He told the Master."

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.13.21"
msgid "“Kiṃcitto tvaṃ, bhikkhū”ti?"
msgstr "“What was your intention, monk?”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.13.22"
msgid "“Anul­lapa­nā­dhip­pāyo ahaṃ, bhagavā”ti."
msgstr "“I didn’t intend to make a claim, Master.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.13.23"
msgid "“Anāpatti, bhikkhu, anul­lapa­nādhip­pāyassā”ti."
msgstr "“There’s no offense for one who doesn’t intend to make a claim.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.13.24"
msgid "(34)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="208"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-pj.4.8.14"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.741"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.14.1"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena sambahulā bhikkhū katikaṃ katvā aññatarasmiṃ āvāse "
"vassaṃ upagacchiṃsu—"
msgstr ""
"At one time a number of monks entered the rainy season residence in a "
"certain monastery, making this agreement:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.14.2"
msgid "“yo imamhā āvāsā paṭhamaṃ pakkamissati taṃ mayaṃ arahāti jānissāmā”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Whomever sets out from this monastery first, we’ll know him as a perfected "
"one.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.14.3"
msgid "Aññataro bhikkhu—"
msgstr "One of the monks thought,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.14.4"
msgid "“maṃ arahāti jānantū”ti,"
msgstr "“Let them know me as a perfected one,”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.14.5"
msgid "tamhā āvāsā paṭhamaṃ pakkāmi."
msgstr "and he set out first from that monastery."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.14.6"
msgid "Tassa kukkuccaṃ ahosi … pe …"
msgstr "He became remorseful …"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs8.14.7"
msgid "“āpattiṃ tvaṃ, bhikkhu, āpanno pārājikan”ti."
msgstr "“You’ve committed an offense entailing expulsion.”"

