msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.1.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Case details, part 2"

#. </h3><p><a class="sc" id="209"></a><a class="pts-cs-empty" id="bu-pj.4.9"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-pj.4.9.1"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.742"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.1.1"
msgid ""
"Tena samayena buddho bhagavā rājagahe viharati veḷuvane kalanda­ka­nivāpe."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying at Rājagaha in the Bamboo Grove, the "
"squirrel sanctuary,"

#. <a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.181"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.1.2"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā ca lakkhaṇo āyasmā ca mahāmoggallāno "
"gijjhakūṭe pabbate viharanti."
msgstr ""
"while Venerable Lakkhaṇa and Venerable Mahāmoggallāna were staying on Mount "
"Vulture Peak."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.1.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā mahāmoggallāno pubbaṇ­ha­samayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaraṃ "
"ādāya yenāyasmā lakkhaṇo tenupasaṅkami;"
msgstr ""
"One morning Mahāmoggallāna robed up, took his bowl and robe, approached "
"Lakkhaṇa,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.1.4"
msgid "upasaṅkamitvā āyasmantaṃ lakkhaṇaṃ etadavoca—"
msgstr "and said,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.1.5"
msgid "“āyāmāvuso lakkhaṇa, rājagahaṃ piṇḍāya pavisissāmā”ti."
msgstr "“Lakkhaṇa, let’s enter Rājagaha for almsfood.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.1.6"
msgid ""
"“Evamāvuso”ti kho āyasmā lakkhaṇo āyasmato ­mahā­mog­gallā­nassa paccassosi."
msgstr "“Yes.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="210"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.743"></a><a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.105"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.1.7"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā mahāmoggallāno gijjhakūṭā pabbatā orohanto aññatarasmiṃ "
"padese sitaṃ pātvākāsi."
msgstr ""
"As they were descending from Mount Vulture Peak, Mahāmoggallāna smiled at a "
"certain place."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.1.8"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā lakkhaṇo āyasmantaṃ ­mahā­mog­gallā­naṃ etadavoca—"
msgstr "Lakkhaṇa asked him,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.1.9"
msgid "“ko nu kho, āvuso moggallāna, hetu ko paccayo sitassa pātukammāyā”ti?"
msgstr "“Why are you smiling?”"

#. </p><p>
#. VAR: etassa pañhassa → paṇhassa byākaraṇāya (s1-3)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.1.10"
msgid "“Akālo kho, āvuso lakkhaṇa, etassa pañhassa."
msgstr "“This isn’t the right time to reply."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.1.11"
msgid "Bhagavato maṃ santike etaṃ pañhaṃ pucchā”ti."
msgstr "Please ask me in the presence of the Master.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="211"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-pj.4.9.2"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.744"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.2.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā ca lakkhaṇo āyasmā ca mahāmoggallāno rājagahe piṇḍāya "
"caritvā pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍa­pāta­paṭik­kantā yena bhagavā tenu­pasaṅka­miṃsu;"
msgstr ""
"Then, after their meal and after returning from almsround, Lakkhaṇa and "
"Mahāmoggallāna approached the Master"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.2.2"
msgid "upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu."
msgstr "and sat down to one side."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.2.3"
msgid ""
"Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā lakkhaṇo āyasmantaṃ ­mahā­mog­gallā­naṃ "
"etadavoca—"
msgstr "And Lakkhaṇa said to Mahāmoggallāna:"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.2.4"
msgid ""
"“idhāyasmā mahāmoggallāno gijjhakūṭā pabbatā orohanto aññatarasmiṃ padese "
"sitaṃ pātvākāsi."
msgstr ""
"“Just now, as you were descending from Mount Vulture Peak, you smiled at a "
"certain place."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.2.5"
msgid "Ko nu kho, āvuso moggallāna, hetu ko paccayo sitassa pātukammāyā”ti?"
msgstr "Why was that?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.182"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.2.6"
msgid ""
"“Idhāhaṃ, āvuso, gijjhakūṭā pabbatā orohanto addasaṃ aṭṭhi­ka­saṅ­kha­likaṃ "
"vehāsaṃ gacchantiṃ."
msgstr ""
"“As I was coming down from Mount Vulture Peak, I saw a skeleton flying "
"through the air."

#. VAR: vituḍenti → vitudanti (bj) | vitudenti vitacchenti virājenti (s1-3) | vitudenti (pts1)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.2.7"
msgid ""
"Tamenaṃ gijjhāpi kākāpi kulalāpi anupatitvā anupatitvā phāsu­ḷanta­rikāhi "
"vituḍenti."
msgstr ""
"Vultures, crows, and hawks were in close pursuit of it, striking it between "
"the ribs,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.2.8"
msgid "Sā sudaṃ aṭṭassaraṃ karoti."
msgstr "while it uttered cries of distress."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.2.9"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, āvuso, etadahosi—"
msgstr "And I thought"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.2.10"
msgid ""
"‘acchariyaṃ vata bho, abbhutaṃ vata bho, evarūpopi nāma satto bhavissati."
msgstr "how amazing and astonishing it is that such a being should exist,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.2.11"
msgid "Evarūpopi nāma yakkho bhavissati."
msgstr "such a spirit,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.2.12"
msgid "Evarūpopi nāma atta­bhāvap­paṭi­lābho bhavissatī’”ti."
msgstr "such a state of existence.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.2.13"
msgid "Bhikkhū ujjhāyanti khiyyanti vipācenti—"
msgstr "The monks complained and criticized him,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.2.14"
msgid "“uttari­manus­sa­dhammaṃ āyasmā mahāmoggallāno ullapatī”ti."
msgstr "“Venerable Mahāmoggallāna is claiming a superhuman ability.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="212"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.745"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.2.15"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi—"
msgstr "The Master then said to them:"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.2.16"
msgid "“cakkhubhūtā vata, bhikkhave, sāvakā viharanti."
msgstr "“There are disciples who have vision"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.2.17"
msgid "Ñāṇabhūtā vata, bhikkhave, sāvakā viharanti."
msgstr "and knowledge,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.2.18"
msgid ""
"Yatra hi nāma sāvako evarūpaṃ ñassati vā dakkhati vā sakkhiṃ vā karissati."
msgstr "and they can see, know, and witness such things."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.2.19"
msgid "Pubbeva me so, bhikkhave, satto diṭṭho ahosi."
msgstr "I too, monks, have seen that being,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.2.20"
msgid "Api cāhaṃ na byākāsiṃ."
msgstr "but I didn’t speak about it."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.2.21"
msgid "Ahañcetaṃ byākareyyaṃ pare ca me na saddaheyyuṃ."
msgstr "If I had, others wouldn’t have believed me,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.2.22"
msgid "Ye me na saddaheyyuṃ tesaṃ taṃ assa dīgharattaṃ ahitāya dukkhāya."
msgstr "and that would have been for their harm and suffering for long time."

#. <a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.183"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.2.23"
msgid "Eso, bhikkhave, satto imasmiṃyeva rājagahe goghātako ahosi."
msgstr "That being was a cattle-butcher in this very Rājagaha."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.2.24"
msgid ""
"So tassa kammassa vipākena bahūni vassāni bahūni vassasatāni bahūni "
"vassasahassāni bahūni vassa­sata­sahas­sāni niraye paccitvā tasseva kammassa "
"vipākāvasesena evarūpaṃ atta­bhāvap­paṭi­lābhaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti."
msgstr ""
"As a result of his deeds, he was tormented in hell for many years, for many "
"hundreds of years, for many thousands of years, for many hundreds of "
"thousands of years. And now, because of the remaining result of his actions, "
"he’s experiencing such an existence."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.2.25"
msgid "Saccaṃ, bhikkhave, moggallāno āha."
msgstr "Moggallāna spoke truthfully."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.2.26"
msgid "Anāpatti, bhikkhave, moggallānassā”ti."
msgstr "There’s no offense for Moggallāna.”"

