"head in a pit of dung, eating dung with both hands …”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.57"
msgid "eso, bhikkhave, satto imasmiṃyeva rājagahe duṭṭhabrāhmaṇo ahosi."
msgstr "“… That being, monks, was a wicked brahmin in this very Rājagaha."

#. VAR: doṇiyo → doṇiyā (si, s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.58"
msgid ""
"So kassapassa sammā­sambud­dhassa pāvacane bhikkhusaṃghaṃ bhattena "
"nimantetvā doṇiyo gūthassa pūrāpetvā kālaṃ ārocāpetvā etadavoca—"
msgstr ""
"At the time of Kassapa, the fully Awakened One, he invited the Order of "
"monks to a meal. He filled a trough with dung, announced the time, and said,"

#. VAR: ato → ito (s1-3) | aho (pts1)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.59"
msgid "‘ato, bhonto, yāvadatthaṃ bhuñjantu ceva harantu cā’”ti … pe …."
msgstr "‘Sirs, eat as much as you like and take the rest away with you.’ …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.60"
msgid "(47)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="224"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.757"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.61"
msgid ""
"“Idhāhaṃ, āvuso, gijjhakūṭā pabbatā orohanto addasaṃ nicchaviṃ itthiṃ "
"vehāsaṃ gacchantiṃ."
msgstr ""
"“As I was coming down from Mount Vulture Peak, I saw a flayed woman flying "
"through the air."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.62"
msgid ""
"Tamenaṃ gijjhāpi kākāpi kulalāpi anupatitvā anupatitvā vitacchenti "
"vibhajjenti."
msgstr ""
"Vultures, crows, and hawks were in close pursuit of her, tearing at her and "
"pulling her to pieces,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.63"
msgid "Sā sudaṃ aṭṭassaraṃ karoti … pe …"
msgstr "while she uttered cries of distress. …” …"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.64"
msgid "esā, bhikkhave, itthī imasmiṃyeva rājagahe aticārinī ahosi … pe …."
msgstr "“… That woman, monks, was an adulteress in this very Rājagaha. …”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.65"
msgid "(48)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="225"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.758"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.66"
msgid ""
"“Idhāhaṃ, āvuso, gijjhakūṭā pabbatā orohanto addasaṃ itthiṃ duggandhaṃ "
"maṅguliṃ vehāsaṃ gacchantiṃ."
msgstr ""
"“As I was coming down from Mount Vulture Peak, I saw a foul-smelling and "
"ugly woman flying through the air."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.67"
msgid ""
"Tamenaṃ gijjhāpi kākāpi kulalāpi anupatitvā anupatitvā vitacchenti "
"vibhajjenti."
msgstr ""
"Vultures, crows, and hawks were in close pursuit of her, tearing at her and "
"pulling her to pieces,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.68"
msgid "Sā sudaṃ aṭṭassaraṃ karoti … pe …"
msgstr "while she uttered cries of distress. …” …"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.69"
msgid "esā, bhikkhave, itthī imasmiṃyeva rājagahe ikkhaṇikā ahosi … pe …."
msgstr "“… That woman, monks, was a fortune-teller in this very Rājagaha. …”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.70"
msgid "(49)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="226"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.759"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.71"
msgid ""
"“Idhāhaṃ, āvuso, gijjhakūṭā pabbatā orohanto addasaṃ itthiṃ uppakkaṃ "
"okiliniṃ okiriniṃ vehāsaṃ gacchantiṃ."
msgstr ""
"“As I was coming down from Mount Vulture Peak, I saw a woman flying through "
"the air who was roasting, sweltering, and sooty."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.72"
msgid "Sā sudaṃ aṭṭassaraṃ karoti … pe …"
msgstr ""
"Vultures, crows, and hawks were in close pursuit of her, tearing at her and "
"pulling her to pieces, while she uttered cries of distress. …” …"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.73"
msgid "esā, bhikkhave, itthī kāliṅgassa rañño aggamahesī ahosi."
msgstr "“… That woman, monks, was the chief queen of the King of Kāliṅga."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.74"
msgid "Sā issāpakatā sapattiṃ aṅgārakaṭāhena okiri … pe …."
msgstr ""
"Because of jealousy, she threw out her rival and poured a pan of burning "
"coals over her. …”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.75"
msgid "(50)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="227"></a><a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.187"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.760"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.76"
msgid ""
"“Idhāhaṃ, āvuso, gijjhakūṭā pabbatā orohanto addasaṃ asīsakaṃ kabandhaṃ "
"vehāsaṃ gacchantaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“As I was coming down from Mount Vulture Peak, I saw the headless trunk of a "
"body flying through the air,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.77"
msgid "Tassa ure akkhīni ceva honti mukhañca."
msgstr "with eyes and mouth on its chest."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.78"
msgid ""
"Tamenaṃ gijjhāpi kākāpi kulalāpi anupatitvā anupatitvā vitacchenti "
"vibhajjenti."
msgstr ""
"Vultures, crows, and hawks were in close pursuit of it, tearing at it and "
"pulling it to pieces,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.79"
msgid "So sudaṃ aṭṭassaraṃ karoti … pe …"
msgstr "while it uttered cries of distress. …” …"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.80"
msgid ""
"eso, bhikkhave, satto imasmiṃyeva rājagahe hāriko nāma coraghātako ahosi … "
"pe …."
msgstr ""
"“… That being, monks, was an executioner called Hārika in this very "
"Rājagaha. …”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.81"
msgid "(51)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="228"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.761"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.82"
msgid ""
"“Idhāhaṃ, āvuso, gijjhakūṭā pabbatā orohanto addasaṃ bhikkhuṃ vehāsaṃ "
"gacchantaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“As I was coming down from Mount Vulture Peak, I saw a monk flying through "
"the air."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.83"
msgid ""
"Tassa saṅghāṭipi ādittā sampajjalitā sajotibhūtā, pattopi āditto "
"sampajjalito sajotibhūto, kāya­bandha­nampi ādittaṃ sampajjalitaṃ "
"sajotibhūtaṃ, kāyopi āditto sampajjalito sajotibhūto."
msgstr ""
"His outer robe was ablaze and burning, as were his bowl, his belt, and his "
"body."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.84"
msgid "So sudaṃ aṭṭassaraṃ karoti … pe …"
msgstr "He uttered cries of distress. …” …"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.85"
msgid ""
"eso, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kassapassa sammā­sambud­dhassa pāvacane pāpabhikkhu "
"ahosi … pe …."
msgstr ""
"“… During the time of the Buddha Kassapa’s dispensation, that monk was a bad "
"monk.” …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.86"
msgid "(52)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="229"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.762"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.87"
msgid "“Idhāhaṃ, āvuso, gijjhakūṭā pabbatā orohanto addasaṃ bhikkhuniṃ …"
msgstr "“As I was coming down from Mount Vulture Peak, I saw a nun …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.88"
msgid "addasaṃ sikkhamānaṃ …"
msgstr "I saw a trainee nun …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.89"
msgid "addasaṃ sāmaṇeraṃ …"
msgstr "I saw a novice monk …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.90"
msgid "addasaṃ sāmaṇeriṃ vehāsaṃ gacchantiṃ."
msgstr "I saw a novice nun flying through the air."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.91"
msgid ""
"Tassā saṅghāṭipi ādittā sampajjalitā sajotibhūtā, pattopi āditto "
"sampajjalito sajotibhūto, kāya­bandha­nampi ādittaṃ sampajjalitaṃ "
"sajotibhūtaṃ, kāyopi āditto sampajjalito sajotibhūto."
msgstr ""
"Her outer robe was ablaze and burning, as were her bowl, her belt, and her "
"body."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.92"
msgid "Sā sudaṃ aṭṭassaraṃ karoti."
msgstr "She uttered cries of distress."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.93"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, āvuso, etadahosi—"
msgstr "And I thought"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.94"
msgid ""
"‘acchariyaṃ vata bho, abbhutaṃ vata bho, evarūpopi nāma satto bhavissati."
msgstr "how amazing and astonishing it is that such a being should exist,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.95"
msgid "Evarūpopi nāma yakkho bhavissati."
msgstr "such a spirit,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.96"
msgid "Evarūpopi nāma atta­bhāvap­paṭi­lābho bhavissatī’”ti."
msgstr "such a state of existence.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.97"
msgid "Bhikkhū ujjhāyanti khiyyanti vipācenti—"
msgstr "The monks complained and criticized him,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.98"
msgid "“uttari­manus­sa­dhammaṃ āyasmā mahāmoggallāno ullapatī”ti."
msgstr "“Venerable Moggallāna is claiming a superhuman ability.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="230"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.763"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.99"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi—"
msgstr "The Master then said to them:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.188"></a><a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.108"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.100"
msgid "“cakkhubhūtā vata, bhikkhave, sāvakā viharanti."
msgstr "“There are disciples who possess vision"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.101"
msgid "Ñāṇabhūtā vata, bhikkhave, sāvakā viharanti."
msgstr "and knowledge,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.102"
msgid ""
"Yatra hi nāma sāvako evarūpaṃ ñassati vā dakkhati vā sakkhiṃ vā karissati."
msgstr "and they can see, know, and witness such things."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.103"
msgid "Pubbeva me sā, bhikkhave, sāmaṇerī diṭṭhā ahosi."
msgstr "I too, monks, have seen this novice nun,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.104"
msgid "Api cāhaṃ na byākāsiṃ."
msgstr "but I didn’t speak about it."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.105"
msgid "Ahañcetaṃ byākareyyaṃ pare ca me na saddaheyyuṃ."
msgstr "If I had, others wouldn’t have believed me,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.106"
msgid "Ye me na saddaheyyuṃ tesaṃ taṃ assa dīgharattaṃ ahitāya dukkhāya."
msgstr "and that would have been for their harm and suffering for a long time."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.107"
msgid ""
"Esā, bhikkhave, sāmaṇerī kassapassa sammā­sambud­dhassa pāvacane "
"pāpasāmaṇerī ahosi."
msgstr ""
"During the time of Buddha Kassapa’s dispensation, that novice nun was a bad "
"novice nun."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.108"
msgid ""
"Sā tassa kammassa vipākena bahūni vassāni bahūni vassasatāni bahūni "
"vassasahassāni bahūni vassa­sata­sahas­sāni niraye paccitvā tasseva kammassa "
"vipākāvasesena evarūpaṃ atta­bhāvap­paṭi­lābhaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti."
msgstr ""
"As a result of her deeds, she was tormented in hell for many years, for many "
"hundreds of years, for many thousands of years, for many hundreds of "
"thousands of years. And now, because of the remaining result of her actions, "
"she’s experiencing such an existence."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.109"
msgid "Saccaṃ, bhikkhave, moggallāno āha."
msgstr "Moggallāna spoke truthfully."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.110"
msgid "Anāpatti, bhikkhave, moggallānassā”ti."
msgstr "There’s no offense for Moggallāna.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.3.111"
msgid "(53–‍56)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="231"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-pj.4.9.4"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.764"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.4.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā mahāmoggallāno bhikkhū āmantesi—"
msgstr "Venerable Mahāmoggallāna said to the monks,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.4.2"
msgid ""
"“yatāyaṃ, āvuso, tapodā sandati so daho acchodako sītodako sātodako setako "
"suppatittho ramaṇīyo pahūta­maccha­kacchapo cakkamattāni ca padumāni "
"pupphantī”ti."
msgstr ""
"“This stream, the Tapodā, flows from a lake with beautiful waters—cool, "
"sweet, and pure—with smooth and pleasant banks, with an abundance of fish "
"and turtles, and with blooming lotuses the size of wheels.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.4.3"
msgid "Bhikkhū ujjhāyanti khiyyanti vipācenti—"
msgstr "The monks complained and criticized him,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.4.4"
msgid "“kathañhi nāma āyasmā mahāmoggallāno evaṃ vakkhati—"
msgstr "“How can Venerable Mahāmoggallāna say"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.4.5"
msgid ""
"‘yatāyaṃ, āvuso, tapodā sandati so daho acchodako sītodako sātodako setako "
"suppatittho ramaṇīyo pahūta­maccha­kacchapo cakkamattāni ca padumāni "
"pupphantī’ti."
msgstr "such a thing?"

#. VAR: kuthitā → kuṭṭhitā (s2, s3)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.4.6"
msgid "Atha ca panāyaṃ tapodā kuthitā sandati."
msgstr "On the contrary, the Tapodā is hot."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.4.7"
msgid "Uttari­manus­sa­dhammaṃ āyasmā mahāmoggallāno ullapatī”ti."
msgstr "Venerable Mahāmoggallāna is claiming a superhuman ability.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.4.8"
msgid "Bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ."
msgstr "And they told the Master."

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.4.9"
msgid ""
"“Yatāyaṃ, bhikkhave, tapodā sandati so daho acchodako sītodako sātodako "
"setako suppatittho ramaṇīyo pahūta­maccha­kacchapo cakkamattāni ca padumāni "
"pupphanti."
msgstr ""
"“Monks, the Tapodā flows from a lake of beautiful waters—with smooth and "
"pleasant banks, with an abundance of fish and turtles, and with blooming "
"lotuses the size of wheels."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.4.10"
msgid ""
"Api cāyaṃ, bhikkhave, tapodā dvinnaṃ mahānirayānaṃ antarikāya āgacchati."
msgstr "But the Tapodā runs between the two great hells;"

#. <a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.189"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.4.11"
msgid "Tenāyaṃ tapodā kuthitā sandati."
msgstr "that’s why it’s hot."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.4.12"
msgid "Saccaṃ, bhikkhave, moggallāno āha."
msgstr "Moggallāna spoke truthfully."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.4.13"
msgid "Anāpatti, bhikkhave, moggallānassā”ti."
msgstr "There’s no offense for Moggallāna.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.4.14"
msgid "(57)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="232"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-pj.4.9.5"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.765"></a> 
#. VAR: ahosi → hoti (bj, s1-3)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.5.1"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena rājā māgadho seniyo bimbisāro licchavīhi saddhiṃ "
"saṅgāmento pabhaggo ahosi."
msgstr ""
"At one time King Seniya Bimbisāra of Magadha was defeated in battle by the "
"Licchavīs."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.5.2"
msgid "Atha rājā pacchā senaṃ saṅkaḍḍhitvā licchavayo parājesi."
msgstr "The King then rallied his army and beat the Licchavīs."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.5.3"
msgid "Saṅgāme ca nandī carati—"
msgstr "People were delighted and the word spread:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.5.4"
msgid "“raññā licchavī pabhaggā”ti."
msgstr "“The Licchavīs have been defeated by the king!”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.5.5"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā mahāmoggallāno bhikkhū āmantesi—"
msgstr "Venerable Mahāmoggallāna said to the monks:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.5.6"
msgid "“rājā, āvuso, licchavīhi pabhaggo”ti."
msgstr "“The King was defeated by the Licchavīs.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.5.7"
msgid "Bhikkhū ujjhāyanti khiyyanti vipācenti—"
msgstr "The monks complained and criticized him,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.5.8"
msgid "“kathañhi nāma āyasmā mahāmoggallāno evaṃ vakkhati—"
msgstr "“How can Venerable Moggallāna say"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.5.9"
msgid "‘rājā, āvuso, licchavīhi pabhaggo’ti."
msgstr "that the King was defeated by the Licchavīs"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.5.10"
msgid "Saṅgāme ca nandī carati—"
msgstr "when people are delighted"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.5.11"
msgid "‘raññā licchavī pabhaggā’ti."
msgstr ""
"and the word is spreading that the Licchavīs have been defeated by the King?"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.5.12"
msgid "Uttari­manus­sa­dhammaṃ āyasmā mahāmoggallāno ullapatī”ti."
msgstr "Venerable Mahāmoggallāna is claiming a superhuman ability.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.5.13"
msgid "Bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ."
msgstr "They told the Master."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.109"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.5.14"
msgid "“Paṭhamaṃ, bhikkhave, rājā licchavīhi pabhaggo."
msgstr "“Monks, first the King was defeated by the Licchavīs,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.5.15"
msgid "Atha rājā pacchā senaṃ saṅkaḍḍhitvā licchavayo parājesi."
msgstr "but then, after he had rallied his army, the King beat the Licchavīs."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.5.16"
msgid "Saccaṃ, bhikkhave, moggallāno āha."
msgstr "Moggallāna spoke truthfully."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.5.17"
msgid "Anāpatti, bhikkhave, moggallānassā”ti."
msgstr "There’s no offense for Moggallāna.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.5.18"
msgid "(58)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="233"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-pj.4.9.6"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.766"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.6.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā mahāmoggallāno bhikkhū āmantesi—"
msgstr "Venerable Mahāmoggallāna said to the monks:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.6.2"
msgid ""
"“idhāhaṃ, āvuso, sappinikāya nadiyā tīre āneñjaṃ samādhiṃ samāpanno nāgānaṃ "
"ogayha uttarantānaṃ koñcaṃ karontānaṃ saddaṃ assosin”ti."
msgstr ""
"“After attaining an imperturbable stillness on the banks of the river "
"Sappinikā, I heard the noise of elephants plunging in, emerging, and "
"trumpeting.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.6.3"
msgid "Bhikkhū ujjhāyanti khiyyanti vipācenti—"
msgstr "The monks complained and criticized him,"

#. <a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.190"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.6.4"
msgid ""
"“kathañhi nāma āyasmā mahāmoggallāno āneñjaṃ samādhiṃ samāpanno saddaṃ "
"sossati."
msgstr "“How can Venerable Mahāmoggallāna say such a thing?"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.6.5"
msgid "Uttari­manus­sa­dhammaṃ āyasmā mahāmoggallāno ullapatī”ti."
msgstr "He’s claiming a superhuman ability.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.6.6"
msgid "Bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ."
msgstr "They told the Master."

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.6.7"
msgid "“Attheso, bhikkhave, samādhi so ca kho aparisuddho."
msgstr "“Monks, there is such a stillness, but it’s not wholly purified."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.6.8"
msgid "Saccaṃ, bhikkhave, moggallāno āha."
msgstr "Moggallāna spoke truthfully."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.6.9"
msgid "Anāpatti, bhikkhave, moggallānassā”ti."
msgstr "There’s no offense for Moggallāna.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.6.10"
msgid "(59)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="234"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-pj.4.9.7"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.767"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.7.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā sobhito bhikkhū āmantesi—"
msgstr "Venerable Sobhita said to the monks,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.7.2"
msgid "“ahaṃ, āvuso, pañca kappasatāni anussarāmī”ti."
msgstr "“I can recall five hundred eons.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.7.3"
msgid "Bhikkhū ujjhāyanti khiyyanti vipācenti—"
msgstr "The monks complained and criticized him,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.7.4"
msgid "“kathañhi nāma āyasmā sobhito evaṃ vakkhati—"
msgstr "“How can Venerable Sobhita say"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.7.5"
msgid "‘ahaṃ, āvuso, pañca kappasatāni anussarāmī’ti."
msgstr "that he can recall five hundred eons?"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.7.6"
msgid "Uttari­manus­sa­dhammaṃ āyasmā sobhito ullapatī”ti."
msgstr "He’s claiming a superhuman ability.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.7.7"
msgid "Bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ."
msgstr "They told the Master."

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.7.8"
msgid "“Atthesā, bhikkhave, sobhitassa."
msgstr "“Monks, Sobhita has this ability,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.7.9"
msgid "Sā ca kho ekāyeva jāti."
msgstr "and that was just one birth."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.7.10"
msgid "Saccaṃ, bhikkhave, sobhito āha."
msgstr "Sobhita spoke truthfully."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.7.11"
msgid "Anāpatti, bhikkhave, sobhitassā”ti."
msgstr "There’s no offense for Sobhita.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.7.12"
msgid "(60)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p class="endsutta"><a class="sc" id="235"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.768"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.7.13"
msgid "Catut­tha­pā­rāji­kaṃ samattaṃ."
msgstr "The fourth offense entailing expulsion is finished."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="236"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.769"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.7.14"
msgid "Uddiṭṭhā kho āyasmanto cattāro pārājikā dhammā,"
msgstr "“Venerables, the four rules entailing expulsion have been recited."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.7.15"
msgid ""
"yesaṃ bhikkhu aññataraṃ vā aññataraṃ vā āpajjitvā na labhati bhikkhūhi "
"saddhiṃ saṃvāsaṃ,"
msgstr ""
"If a monk commits any one of them, he is no longer part of the community of "
"monks."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.7.16"
msgid "yathā pure tathā pacchā, pārājiko hoti asaṃvāso."
msgstr "As before, so after, he’s expelled and excluded from the community."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.7.17"
msgid "Tatthāyasmante pucchāmi—"
msgstr "In regard to this I ask you,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.7.18"
msgid "“kaccittha parisuddhā”?"
msgstr "‘Are you pure in this?’"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.7.19"
msgid "Dutiyampi pucchāmi—"
msgstr "A second time I ask,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.7.20"
msgid "“kaccittha parisuddhā”?"
msgstr "‘Are you pure in this?’"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.7.21"
msgid "Tatiyampi pucchāmi—"
msgstr "A third time I ask,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.7.22"
msgid "“kaccittha parisuddhā”?"
msgstr "‘Are you pure in this?’"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.7.23"
msgid "Pari­sud­dhet­thā­yasmanto, tasmā tuṇhī,"
msgstr "You are pure in this and therefore silent."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.7.24"
msgid "evametaṃ dhārayāmīti."
msgstr "I will remember it thus.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection"><a class="sc" id="237"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.770"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.7.25"
msgid "Pārājikaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ."
msgstr "The rules entailing expulsion are finished."

#. </p><p class="endsection summary"><a class="sc" id="238"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.771"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.7.26"
msgid "Tassuddānaṃ"
msgstr "This is the summary:"

#. </p><div class="uddana"><p><a class="sc" id="239"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.772"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.7.27"
msgid "Methu­nādinnā­dānañca,"
msgstr "Sexual intercourse, and stealing,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.7.28"
msgid "­manus­sa­vigga­huttari;"
msgstr "Person, super;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.7.29"
msgid "Pārājikāni cattāri,"
msgstr "The four offenses entailing expulsion—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.7.30"
msgid "chejjavatthū asaṃsayāti."
msgstr "The foundation is definitively cut off."

#. </p></div><p class="endsection"><a class="sc" id="240"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.773"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pj4:pts-cs9.7.31"
msgid "Pārājikakaṇḍaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ."
msgstr "The chapter on offenses entailing expulsion is finished."

